name: Primordial Womb
description:
As we approach the center of the primordial womb, it would be as if we were approaching eternity. At its most basic level, if the primordial womb is perceived to be made up of particles called quarks, then these particles are akin to embryos. Each atom is its own conceptus, a thought never thought before, a story never written before.

Dark chamomile haze

Licorice centre

Cherry candy Blood

Synesthetic review by Jahnu Nyamu
